 "en-US", numberOfReviews: "95716", latitude: "40.7484", rating: "4.5", description: "The Empire State Building is the World's Most Famous Building. It rises 1,454 ft from ground to antenna & features the only 360 degree open-air vantage point of Midtown. The 86th & 102nd Fl Observatories are open daily, see esbnyc.com for hours. On a clear day you can see up to 6 states. The brand-new 2nd floor museum (included in all ticket options) offers guests 10,000 sq ft of interactive exhibits that invite visitors on a journey beginning from the building’s construction to its current place in pop culture. The 102nd Fl Obs features floor-to-ceiling windows and a glass elevator with sound & light experience. It is the jewel of NYC. All signage, audio & exhibits in the building are available in 9 languages. We offer free Wi-Fi. The 34th St Lobby entrance features a grand staircase with a 2-story architectural model of the bldg & a high-tech LED exhibit that celebrates lighting ceremonies performed by famous, celebrity guests. Express guests receive red carpet VIP treatment.", visit_duration: "3.0", addressObj: "{\"street1\": \"20 West 34th Street\", \"street2\": null, \"city\": \"New York City\", \"state\": \"NY\", \"country\": \"United States\", \"postalcode\": \"10001\"}", offerGroup: "{\"lowestPrice\": \"$4.69\", \"offerList\": [{\"url\": \"https://www.tripadvisor.com/Commerce?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.viator.com%2Ftours%2FNew-York-City%2FEmpire-State-Building-Tickets-Observatory-Ticket%2Fd687-2194EMPIRE%3Feap%3Dtripadvisor-main-11383%26aid%3Dtripen1&partnerKey=1&urlKey=77eab68b9c6510210&logme=true&uidparam=refid&attrc=true&Provider=Viator&area=viator_multi&slot=1&cnt=1&geo=104365&clt=TD&from=api&nt=true\", \"price\": \"$47.91\", \"roundedUpPrice\": \"$48\", \"offerType\": null, \"title\": \"NYC Empire State Building Admission Ticket\", \"productCode\": \"2194EMPIRE\", \"partner\": \"Viator\", \"imageUrl\": \"https://media.tacdn.com/media/attractions-splice-spp-360x240/0d/0d/9a/